<h4><strong>How to use</strong></h4>
The Sattvic Foods Coconut Flour can be used to make anything from delightful cakes to mouth watering cookies.

Baking requires 1/4 cup to 1/3 cup of coconut flour for 1 cup grain-based flour. For frying or sauteing it can be used in amounts equal to that of wheat flour.

A single 2 Tbsp serving of coconut flour delivers 5 grams of fiber with only 8 grams of carbs and no gluten, making it ideal for those on a Paleo or low carb diet.

